Steps to Install SASS:

1. Ensure Node.js is installed:
   - Node.js version checked: node -v
   - npm version checked: npm -v

2. Install SASS globally:
   - Ran: npm install -g sass
   - Installed version: 1.92.1

3. Verify installation:
   - Ran: sass --version
   - Output: 1.92.1 compiled with dart2js 3.9.2
   - SASS is ready to compile .scss files into CSS
